      **Benefits:**
      - Higher recall@k (5-10% improvement)
      - Fewer search iterations
      - Better graph connectivity
      - Reduced local minima
    |
    cons: |md
      **Costs:**
      - Slightly slower construction
      - More distance computations
      - May reject closer neighbors
      - Implementation complexity
    |
